## Nightly Maintenance

<!-- Memory maintenance that runs after the last checkpoint of each day. -->
<!-- This keeps MEMORY.md healthy and prevents context bloat. -->
<!-- These rules should match the promotion/demotion config in MEMORY.md. -->

Run after last checkpoint of the day:

1. **Demotion:** Any entry in MEMORY.md older than {{MEMORY_DEMOTION_DAYS}} days and not marked [permanent] — move to `memory/archive.md`.
2. **Promotion:** Read last 3 daily logs. Any topic in 2+ logs but NOT in MEMORY.md — add it (1-2 lines).
3. **Cap check:** MEMORY.md must stay under {{MEMORY_MAX_LINES}} lines. If over, demote oldest non-permanent entries.
4. **Bank update:** New decisions go to `memory/bank/decisions.md`. New research goes to `memory/bank/research.md`.
5. **Integrity ({{INTEGRITY_CHECK_CADENCE}}):** Check for contradictions between MEMORY.md, daily logs, and bank. Write to `memory/conflicts.md` if found.
6. Log all maintenance actions to daily log under `## Nightly Memory Maintenance`.

